<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 37 (October 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Bolt (Q)</b></li><ul><li> Fixed a bug where this ability could be used while rooted.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 36.1 (October 7, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>On the House(E)</b></li><ul><li> The maximum base damage of this ability has been increased to 60/95/130/165/200, up from 50/80/110/140/170.</li><li> The minimum base damage of this ability has been increased to 40/65/90/115/140, up from 35/50/65/80/95.</li></ul><li><b>Reckoning (R)</b></li><ul><li> The basic attack damage bonus granted by this ability has been increased to 50/75/100, up from 35/60/85.</li></ul></ul>